OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny spells along with
OL,7,Fscattered showers. These will turn
OL,8,Fheavy this afternoon with some hail
OL,9,Fand thunder. Warm in any brightness.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be partly
OL,12,Fcloudy with scattered showers, heavy
OL,13,Fat first. Then the rest of the night
OL,14,Fwill see variable amounts of cloud and
OL,15,Fsome showery rain.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,18,Fand a few showers, these becoming
OL,19,Flighter and fewer in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
