OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy on Thursday with early rain,
OL,7,Fand again later. Mainly dry, bright
OL,8,Fand warm on Friday. Chance of early
OL,9,Frain on Saturday, otherwise dry.
